                        Some tasks such as loading new data or running models require considerable time to complete and are spawned as seperate processes on the TDM server. <br><br>
                        This architecture allows the users freedom to start long processes and keep tabs on their progress.
                        <br><br>
                         This page lists currently active jobs, along with progress &amp; status indication as well as a list of finished jobs and their outcome. It also allows you to cancel currently active jobs.
