                            <li><strong>Initializing</strong> - Job is being set up for processing.</li>
                            <li><strong>Processing</strong> - Job is currently being run on the server.</li> 
                            <li><strong>Finishing</strong> - Job is finished and meta data is being saved about the job.</li>
                            <li><strong>Success</strong> - Job has been successfully finished and data is incorporated into TDM</li>
                            <li><strong>Failure</strong> - Job has finished unsuccessfully and will need to be run again.</li>
